DarkMagic 2.2.0
================================================================================
+ Improved TinyMCE theme loading
+ Dark theme for CodeMirror
+ Add a CSS class to the BODY tag indicating the applicable dark mode
# [LOW] Striped tables need alternate color for stripe rows

DarkMagic 2.1.0
================================================================================
+ Support Cassiopeia child templates (at long last!)
+ Using a joomla.asset.json file with the WebAssetManager
~ Update color definitions to allow child Cassiopeia templates to define their own colors

DarkMagic 2.0.3
================================================================================
# [HIGH] Fatal error if TinyMCE dark mode is enabled when “Apply dark theme“ is set to anything but Browser (gh-2)
# [LOW] PHP 8.1 deprecated notice from the color handling code

DarkMagic 2.0.2
================================================================================
+ Support for Joomla 4.1
+ About box in the plugin's configuration page
+ Style the TinyMCE chrome, optionally also the content area.
+ Styling for new module and new task pages
+ Media Manager sidebar background color adjustment.
~ Improved display of plugin options
# [HIGH] Sometimes the CSS might not load at all

DarkMagic 2.0.1
================================================================================
~ Updated for Joomla 4 stable
~ Fully native Joomla 4 plugin

